DESCRIPTION

  XML::Simpler - Simpler API for handling XML

  See 'perldoc XML::Simpler' for more details


PREREQUISITES

  Requires File::Slurp


BUILDING/INSTALLING

  Once the archive is unpacked, use these commands:

      perl Makefile.PL
      make
      make test
      make install


RELEASE HISTORY

  Version 1.00 of XML::Simpler was released on April 1st, 2002


